subject: Found a bug in disease detection
message:
I found an issue where the system incorrectly identifies healthy leaves as diseased. Here are the steps to reproduce:
1. Upload a clear image of a healthy tomato leaf
2. Run detection
3. System shows "Late Blight" with 85% confidence

Expected: Should show "Healthy"
